data.description: 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Brick Ranch in popular Wedgewood Park. This solidly build home features hardwood floors, spacious kitchen, freshly painted walls, and a three season porch.  Large Master bedroom with private bath. Garage is oversized with room for tools and a workbench. Basement is partially finished with an adjacent work room. City water and a duel septic field system keeps your taxes low. Fenced in yard completes this package. Call for your private showing today.
